Story Context
You are working at a company called EventRush, which manages emergency service requests. The
system receives thousands of requests and must prioritize them correctly.
Your task is to build a custom sorting engine using Merge Sort and Quick Sort from scratch.
Important: You are NOT allowed to use any built-in sorting functions.

